    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car that it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a total dream and has been my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
